	<div class="d-flex container flex-column flex-lg-row text-justify">
		<div class="mt-5">
			<h1 id="about-title" class="mt-5">Welcome to the <span>Learn & Earn</span> Contest!</h1>
			<h3 class="mt-5">Where Learning Pays Off<span id="dash">_</span></h3>
			<p>
				Looking for a way to up your skillset while also earning some cash?
			</p>
			<p>
				Students of The Web Developer Bootcamp are now invited to help answer questions in the Q&A as part of a weekly contest.</p>
			<p>
				The three students who answer the most solved questions after 1 week will win $15 (first), $10 (second), and $5 (third).
