			<h3>Contest Rules<span id="dash">_</span></h3>
			<ul>
				<li>You must submit a list of the questions you answered/solved to learntocodeinfoATgmailDOTcom in an email titled: "LEARN AND EARN ENTRY", the monday after each contest week in order to be included in the previous week's contest</li>
